'''''Chronicle of the Years of Fire''''' ( Arabic    ; French   ; aya mazina yombi asobanura "Chronicle of the Year of Embers ") ni filime yamateka yikinamico yo muri Alijeriya yakinwe muri 1975 iyobowe na Mohammed Lakhdar-Hamina<ref>https://www.tiff.net/events/chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire</ref> <ref>https://www.institut-francais.org.uk/cine-lumiere/whats-on/festivals-series/chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire/</ref>. Irerekana Intambara yo kwigenga ya Alijeriya nkuko bigaragara mumaso y'umuhanzi<ref>https://mubi.com/films/chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire</ref><ref>https://mubi.com/films/chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire</ref>.

Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya ''Palme d'Or'' mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 1975<ref>https://africa.film/the-chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire-a-mohammed-lakhdar-hamina-feature-film/</ref> <ref>http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/863603437</ref>.  Yatoranijwe kandi nk'iyinjira muri Alijeriya muri Filime Nziza y'indimi z'amahanga mu bihembo bya 48 bya Academy, ariko ntiyakirwa nk'umukandida.<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire/m0c7_g1?hl=en</ref> <ref>https://screenworlds.org/announcements/chronicles-of-the-years-of-fire-1975-rare-film-screening-at-institut-francaiss-cine-lumiere/</ref>

